dcron - simple cron daemon

info:
Single daemon, config and initscript.
Logs to stdout and syslog.

usage:
usage: dcron [options]
-h              help
-d              daemon
-f <file>       config file

config:
# min,hour,mday,mon,wday,command
10	6	*	*	*	exec ionice -n 2 updatedb
20	6	*	*	*	exec nice -n 10 mandb --quiet
